Didn't know the Avatar mastered a 5th element 🛹 #AvatarTheLastAirbender @AvatarNetflix
#AvatarTheLast Airbender #Aang #AvatarNetflix #TimesSquare #NikonCreators
I spotted Aang from Avatar: The Last Airbender - which I watched on Netflix a few days ago. 
He was skateboarding in Times Square and as a photographer, I had to ask him to do a photoshoot. 
He had a very tight schedule and had to go really soon. I worked really quick and nailed several AMAZING shots. I'm editing the photos and animating the video at the moment, which will be posted in the next video.
sdfsdf
